title: So, Senna's release date
body:
Will we get her on the 10th or the 11th?

Need something to tide me over, seeing as climbing ranked is pointless due to no rewards.

replies.body: The [9.22 patch notes for OCE](https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/patch/patch-922-notes) state that Senna will be released on the 11th November. I did some checking into other regions patch notes and, if I'm not mistaken, she should be available between 2-8am AEDT.

> [{quoted}](name=HeartVine,realm=OCE,application-id=Ntey9fRZ,discussion-id=P416Qdt4,comment-id=0000,timestamp=2019-11-09T11:17:28.258+0000)
>
> The [9.22 patch notes for OCE](https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/patch/patch-922-notes) state that Senna will be released on the 11th November. I did some checking into other regions patch notes and, if I'm not mistaken, she should be available between 2-8am AEDT.

wack. No doubt she won't be activated until the 15th when I'll be off playing decent games.
